{"title":"只为再见到你","date":"2018-04-16T02:46:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 16, 2018","L":"04/16/2018","MM-DD":"04-16"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/OTyetBjp2iDqdV7.jpg","link":"2018/04/16/只为再见到你","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T16:44:18.024Z","content":"<p>张开双眼<br>\n寻不到任何焦点<br>\n思绪万千<br>\n却麻木而空洞</p>\n<p>黑暗中我抱紧了自己的臂膀<br>\n耳边是收音机的白噪<br>\n像是身体深处的隐痛<br>\n无法逃避</p>\n<p>为什么<br>\n我见到了自己同你在一起<br>\n一定是我睡过去了</p>\n<p>我爱上了这空洞的黑暗<br>\n隐痛的白噪<br>\n只为再见到你</p>\n","prev":{"title":"我望着你","link":"2018/04/18/我望着你"},"next":{"title":"我曾去过沙漠","link":"2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/16/只为再见到你/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 11, 2020"}}